::KitKat3::
She made  it to the BlackFortress.  She was out of breath, but glad 
she made it finally. She opened her commlink. "Hello, anyone inside 
the base? It's me, KitKat. Let me in, please."  She transformed into 
bot mode and waited outside.

DarkMouse::
She saw KitKat3 out side, "Welcome back.  You might want to get in 
here, trouble is around." She opened the entrance for KitKat3

::KitKat3::
She walked in, and looked around.  She was impressed with how things 
had changed and how well the Pack had done in her absences.  She went 
down the hall, wondering who she might find. 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

::KitKat2::
She wandered around for a while.  She followed her nose.  She thought 
she was backtracking her own scent, but in actuallity, she was 
following the scent of her now twin.  She followed it to the base, 
but it wasn't the BlackFortress.  She sniffed around and noticed the 
scent of other preds, but none from her pack.  She stood outside the 
entrance and waited.
